/**

export var BasePagerProps = {
    gridCompatibility: true,
    showInfo: false,
    displayMode: "adaptive",
    maxPagesCount: 10,
    pageCount: 10,
    visible: true,
    hasKnownLastPage: true,
    pagesNavigatorVisible: "auto",
